    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Good infrastucture . all the audotorium have AC all builfings are well maintained",
          "name": "Kuntal Bera",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lab , all the labs have suficient space and things of experiment",
          "name": "Kuntal Bera",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our professors are so friendly and they are well-educated enough to solve our doubts",
          "name": "Sohan Giri",
          "course_tag_name": "MA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Peaceful environment, the environment in our college is so peacefull",
          "name": "Sohan Giri",
          "course_tag_name": "MA"
        },
        {
          "text": "First of all in my college registration which is so high then the middle class family is approved by the college is suit of",
          "name": "Biswapratap Mandal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college is so large .Many department is present here .an many cultural programs occur . Teacher student bonding is good . Teacher teach very carefully.",
          "name": "Ritwika Chanda",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college campus is so much beautiful.In our college campus beautiful garden in present including beautiful flowers .",
          "name": "Ritwika Chanda",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the college is clean , all building have good quality RO fecility",
          "name": "Kuntal Bera",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Some department get placement",
