        },
        {
          "text": "Then the practical subject like zoology cost the lot of money",
          "name": "Biswapratap Mandal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our department many instruments of lab is absent ..so some practical is not occur",
          "name": "Ritwika Chanda",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Light is not available in girls bathroom. And bathroom is very dirty.",
          "name": "Ritwika Chanda",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some teacher is not teach carefully . Department room is not available.",
